# Local Agent Skills Repository

The upstream collections with 770+ Agent Skills live in `~/Development/osforge/sources/` (ADR-009; gitignored, disk only).

Skills are best-practice references extracted from official repositories (Anthropic, Vercel, Supabase, Trail of Bits, Cloudflare, Expo, Sentry) and from the community.

**When to consult**: When facing a complex problem in a specific domain (security, React performance, PostgreSQL optimization, fuzzing, etc.), check whether a relevant skill exists before improvising a solution.

